<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="932042" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">与牧师斗，其乐无穷。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/63bf65be90d63ad61f347691eb37c846_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1154" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1154" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/63bf65be90d63ad61f347691eb37c846_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1154" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1154" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/63bf65be90d63ad61f347691eb37c846_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/63bf65be90d63ad61f347691eb37c846_b.jpg"><br><br>不管风吹浪打，胜似闲庭信步。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/94577718de68e9ea1e38565c9fe9b131_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1151" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1151" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/94577718de68e9ea1e38565c9fe9b131_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1151" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1151" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/94577718de68e9ea1e38565c9fe9b131_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/94577718de68e9ea1e38565c9fe9b131_b.jpg"><br><br>宜将剩勇追穷寇，红龙半血再打残。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/dd7fcb8bb51412177e65cb016671f312_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1154" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1154" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/dd7fcb8bb51412177e65cb016671f312_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1154" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1154" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/dd7fcb8bb51412177e65cb016671f312_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/dd7fcb8bb51412177e65cb016671f312_b.jpg"><br><br>三回合太久，发条巨人。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/6257a5d5c3b53a8b8ef501e3df13e105_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1154" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1154" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/6257a5d5c3b53a8b8ef501e3df13e105_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1154" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1154" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/6257a5d5c3b53a8b8ef501e3df13e105_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/6257a5d5c3b53a8b8ef501e3df13e105_b.jpg"><br><br>论持久战：<br><br>几乎打光手牌抢血，对方德鲁伊场面占优，然后他1血来了张生命之树。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e501e1488db58c1e62088884798bccf6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="268" data-rawheight="380" class="content_image" width="268"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="268" data-rawheight="380" class="content_image lazy" width="268" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/e501e1488db58c1e62088884798bccf6_b.jpg"><br><br>小刀清怪，用载人收割机和他纠缠，在牌都快摸光的时候，终于等来了发条巨人。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/fce936eb927d3e8c9623d7b402f60959_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1154" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1154" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/fce936eb927d3e8c9623d7b402f60959_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1154" data-rawheight="689" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1154" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/fce936eb927d3e8c9623d7b402f60959_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/fce936eb927d3e8c9623d7b402f60959_b.jpg"><br><br>数风流人物，还看发条。<br><br>我抠了抠鼻子，深藏功与名。


